sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 사용자
    participant App as 앱
    participant Rechamp as Re챔프
    participant Admin as 관리강의
    participant Champ as 챔프강의
    participant Unified as 통합LCMS
    participant Settle as 정산
    participant Modal as 비교 모달

    U->>App: [비교] 클릭 (강의코드, B2C강의코드)
    App->>App: B2B 강의 행 조회
    App->>Rechamp: getRechampDataByB2CCode
    App->>Admin: getDataById(skinId)
    App->>Champ: getDataByRowNo(champLectureId)
    App->>Unified: getDataByLectureId(adminLectureCode)
    App->>Settle: getStatusByCode(강의코드)
    App->>Modal: 비교 모달 표시
    U->>App: 닫기 클릭/Esc
    App->>Modal: 모달 닫기
